304
00:17:19,890 --> 00:17:20,880
Yes, I know.

305
00:17:30,190 --> 00:17:31,950
Will Jane tell Peak
that we're here to see him?

306
00:17:33,700 --> 00:17:34,930
I think she will.

307
00:17:35,600 --> 00:17:37,250
But whether Peak will come or not
is another matter.

308
00:17:38,070 --> 00:17:39,330
We can only wait for this, right?

309
00:17:42,890 --> 00:17:43,730
Or...

310
