316
00:18:21,620 --> 00:18:23,380
Okay, cover him.

317
00:18:25,240 --> 00:18:26,930
One, two, three.

318
00:18:34,530 --> 00:18:35,400
No way.

319
00:18:36,310 --> 00:18:37,360
I don't think it works.

320
00:18:38,460 --> 00:18:40,220
