everything will be back to the same loop.

321
00:18:40,670 --> 00:18:41,880
It won't help solve the problem.

322
00:18:43,620 --> 00:18:45,210
It will be difficult for Peak and Jane.

323
00:18:47,660 --> 00:18:49,520
Or will we secretly wait to see him?

324
00:19:16,560 --> 00:19:17,780
I'll take a shower now.

325
00:19:18,160 --> 00:19:19,330
You just clean all the dishes.

326
00:19:22,640 --> 00:19:24,730
They came to help you out.

327
00:19:25,770 --> 00:19:26,690
Call them.

328
00:19:27,020 --> 00:19:28,710
It's better if you go to meet them.

329
00:19:32,540 --> 00:19:38,060
(You are not alone.)

330
00:19:50,580 --> 00:19:53,380
(Elizabeth Hotel)

331
00:19:59,670 --> 00:20:01,550
