337
00:20:15,220 --> 00:20:16,750
So, we will get some sleep first.

338
00:20:17,240 --> 00:20:18,670
- All right, see you.
- See you.

339
00:20:19,400 --> 00:20:20,240
Let's go.

340
00:20:51,840 --> 00:20:52,680
Thanwa.

341
00:20:55,620 --> 00:20:56,460
Peak.

342
00:21:11,620 --> 00:21:16,140
"Knock Knock, Boys!"

343
