354
00:22:19,400 --> 00:22:20,950
Okay, apply your skin care to me now.

355
00:22:24,070 --> 00:22:24,910
Come on.

356
00:22:37,160 --> 00:22:38,000
I'll do it now.

357
00:23:03,620 --> 00:23:04,890
Thank you so much.

358
00:23:09,070 --> 00:23:10,920
If you didn't wake me up every morning,

359
00:23:12,080 --> 00:23:13,110
I'd still be

360
00:23:14,010 --> 00:23:15,510
a reckless person

361
00:23:16,910 --> 00:23:18,510
who doesn't want to get up
and go to class.

362
00:23:21,090 --> 00:23:23,380
And I would've dropped out again.

363
00:23:23,960 --> 00:23:24,800
Oh,

364
00:23:25,280 --> 00:23:26,150
you told me you have transferred.

365
00:23:28,120 --> 00:23:28,960
Never mind.

366
00:23:29,780 --> 00:23:31,040
Whatever it is,

367
00:23:32,648 --> 00:23:34,348
I can turn over a new leaf
because of you.

368
00:23:44,590 --> 00:23:45,990
Just thanks to the alarm clock

369
00:23:46,730 --> 00:23:48,740
that is louder than fire alarm.

370
00:23:54,400 --> 00:23:55,240
Do you know?

371
00:23:56,450 --> 00:23:57,980
Since I met you,

372
00:23:58,910 --> 00:24:00,360
I've been very happy.

373
00:24:03,030 --> 00:24:05,150
You make me want to get up
and go to class every morning.

374
00:24:07,020 --> 00:24:08,340
I want to take care of you.

375
00:24:09,950 --> 00:24:11,460
I want to protect you.

376
00:24:14,500 --> 00:24:16,200
And I want to be
the one who teaches you,

377
00:24:16,910 --> 00:24:18,780
and grows old with you.

378
00:25:20,820 --> 00:25:22,160
Every time I think about my mother,

379
00:25:22,820 --> 00:25:24,650
I feel lonely or I have no one,

380
00:25:26,440 --> 00:25:27,810
I look up to the sky.

381
00:25:31,040 --> 00:25:33,390
The moon represents
the longing I have for my mother.

382
00:25:36,520 --> 00:25:37,830
I always come to see my mom,

383
00:25:38,170 --> 00:25:39,560
whenever I feel bad.

384
00:25:44,150 --> 00:25:45,770
When it's a full moon,

385
00:25:46,170 --> 00:25:47,150
I feel that

386
00:25:47,150 --> 00:25:49,380
I get all the love my mom would give me.

387
00:25:58,220 --> 00:25:59,420
But whenever

388
00:26:00,640 --> 00:26:01,480
the sky is dark,

389
00:26:02,470 --> 00:26:04,250
and clouds cover the moon,

390
00:26:05,850 --> 00:26:08,350
I would embrace myself
and try to find comfort.

391
00:26:12,620 --> 00:26:14,340
You have such vivid imagination.

392
00:26:19,320 --> 00:26:20,160
Mom.

393
00:26:21,440 --> 00:26:22,380
This is Thanwa.

394
00:26:23,380 --> 00:26:25,870
Thanwa, I want to introduce my mom to you.

395
00:26:29,530 --> 00:26:30,710
I promise that I will try my best
to take care of Peak.

396
00:26:34,310 --> 00:26:36,990
I won't let anything

397
00:26:36,990 --> 00:26:39,600
happen to him.

398
00:26:40,010 --> 00:26:41,210
You are crazy just like me.

399
00:26:42,690 --> 00:26:43,530
Come on.

400
00:26:55,700 --> 00:26:56,540
I am scared.

401
00:26:59,910 --> 00:27:01,060
No need to feel scared.

402
00:27:01,950 --> 00:27:03,320
Whatever happens,

403
00:27:03,930 --> 00:27:05,250
I will always be by your side.

404
00:27:06,970 --> 00:27:09,090
It's a moment of truth for you.

405
00:27:14,140 --> 00:27:15,580
Don't you run away from me.

406
00:27:27,100 --> 00:27:28,300
Can you take me to my room?

407
00:27:30,390 --> 00:27:31,230
All right.

408
00:27:52,450 --> 00:27:53,290
Here is my room.

409
00:27:54,520 --> 00:27:55,920
Thanks a lot for taking me to my room.

410
00:27:56,800 --> 00:27:57,710
You should go home now.

411
00:28:01,150 --> 00:28:02,240
I don't want to.

412
00:28:03,720 --> 00:28:04,790
You have to.

413
00:28:05,250 --> 00:28:06,140
Just go home.

414
00:28:06,610 --> 00:28:07,450
Sweet dreams.

415
00:28:16,130 --> 00:28:17,450
If I want to have sweet dreams,

416
00:28:19,940 --> 00:28:21,460
I need you by my side.

417
00:28:56,060 --> 00:28:57,030
Just like what I have said,

418
00:28:58,250 --> 00:28:59,670
I will have sweet dreams

419
00:29:01,060 --> 00:29:02,600
if you are by my side.

420
00:29:04,540 --> 00:29:05,470
And you need to stay close.

421
00:29:16,240 --> 00:29:17,100
Thanks a lot.

422
00:29:21,130 --> 00:29:21,970
About what?

423
00:29:23,470 --> 00:29:24,910
The message you sent to me

424
00:29:26,460 --> 00:29:28,290
made me feel that I was not alone.

425
00:29:30,320 --> 00:29:31,160
Actually,

426
00:29:33,150 --> 00:29:35,120
I feel really bad

427
00:29:35,380 --> 00:29:36,720
for causing everyone trouble.

428
00:29:38,290 --> 00:29:39,480
Because you all wait for me to be ready.

429
00:29:41,700 --> 00:29:43,600
But I also feel good

430
00:29:45,770 --> 00:29:47,530
that I have many friends who understand me.

431
00:29:47,840 --> 00:29:49,040
They all support me.

432
00:29:52,000 --> 00:29:53,440
You're slow to find it out.

433
00:30:03,120 --> 00:30:05,080
Why did everyone have to do this to me?

434
00:30:06,430 --> 00:30:07,850
Before I just ran away,

435
00:30:08,190 --> 00:30:09,030
I was scared.

436
00:30:09,840 --> 00:30:11,430
I have always tried to escape.

437
00:30:13,390 --> 00:30:14,930
But instead, everyone understood me

438
00:30:16,230 --> 00:30:17,430
and tried to stand by me.

439
00:30:21,190 --> 00:30:22,440
I was so terrible, right?

440
00:30:23,850 --> 00:30:24,690
Not at all.

441
00:30:25,810 --> 00:30:27,980
You did it out of love, right?

442
00:30:31,620 --> 00:30:33,800
But my love hurts everyone

443
00:30:34,880 --> 00:30:36,000
and causes them trouble.

444
00:30:37,060 --> 00:30:38,040
Latte,

445
00:30:40,070 --> 00:30:40,910
Almond,

446
00:30:42,810 --> 00:30:43,650
Jane,

447
00:30:44,960 --> 00:30:45,800
and you.

448
00:30:48,010 --> 00:30:49,200
Don't you think I am selfish?

449
00:30:51,840 --> 00:30:52,680
Yes.

450
00:30:54,240 --> 00:30:55,650
Maybe you're selfish,

451
00:30:56,690 --> 00:30:58,620
but that's because you love
your father very much, right?

452
00:31:00,780 --> 00:31:02,410
You are afraid that he will be sad.

453
00:31:03,520 --> 00:31:04,800
But it doesn't matter at all.

454
00:31:05,310 --> 00:31:07,060
You haven't tried talking it out yet.

455
00:31:07,480 --> 00:31:09,460
How do you know what he thinks about this?

456
00:31:17,740 --> 00:31:19,980
I shouldn't have let it get to this point.

457
00:31:22,280 --> 00:31:23,910
Is it too late to say it?

458
00:31:25,480 --> 00:31:26,320
No.

459
00:31:27,940 --> 00:31:29,270
And you don't have to be afraid.

460
00:31:31,180 --> 00:31:32,320
I will be by your side.

461
00:31:38,560 --> 00:31:39,680
Not just me,

462
00:31:40,880 --> 00:31:42,680
everyone will be by your side, Peak.

463
00:31:46,170 --> 00:31:48,630
When you turn around,
you will see me stand by you.

464
00:31:51,920 --> 00:31:52,760
Thanks.

465
00:31:57,720 --> 00:31:59,100
Don't run away again.

466
00:32:07,060 --> 00:32:07,900
Never.

467
00:32:10,500 --> 00:32:11,380
From now on,

468
00:32:13,160 --> 00:32:14,270
I won't run away again.

469
00:32:39,340 --> 00:32:40,720
Can I sleep with you tonight?

470
00:32:43,480 --> 00:32:45,110
Father Dilok will complain.

471
00:32:48,250 --> 00:32:49,510
We'll worry about that tomorrow.

472
00:32:51,970 --> 00:32:53,560
Today I will not escape my feelings.

473
00:32:55,440 --> 00:32:56,640
I want to be here

474
00:32:59,600 --> 00:33:00,440
with you.

475
00:33:57,300 --> 00:34:00,580
(Dad is calling)

476
00:34:06,280 --> 00:34:07,210
Thanwa.

477
00:34:07,210 --> 00:34:08,520
Open the door.

478
00:34:08,790 --> 00:34:10,360
- Just a second.
- Thanwa.

479
00:34:10,460 --> 00:34:11,350
What's the matter?

480
00:34:11,590 --> 00:34:12,520
Thanwa.

481
00:34:13,410 --> 00:34:17,170
- About Peak...
- I am here!

482
00:34:17,770 --> 00:34:19,640
Peak, your dad is very angry.

483
00:34:19,890 --> 00:34:21,890
