he couldn't contact you.

484
00:34:22,680 --> 00:34:23,860
But here you are.

485
00:34:26,260 --> 00:34:27,210
Just a second.

486
00:34:30,760 --> 00:34:31,600
Darn it!

487
00:34:33,320 --> 00:34:34,390
My phone died last night.

488
00:34:36,010 --> 00:34:36,850
So, come on.

489
00:34:37,490 --> 00:34:38,710
Go back to your dad.

490
00:34:40,070 --> 00:34:41,240
Oh, okay.

491
00:34:44,560 --> 00:34:45,400
- You...
- What?

492
00:34:45,680 --> 00:34:46,560
Shall we go together?

493
00:34:51,880 --> 00:34:54,480
Go. Let's go now.

494
00:35:12,460 --> 00:35:13,300
Peak.

495
00:35:15,290 --> 00:35:16,420
You all wait in the car.

496
00:35:17,280 --> 00:35:18,950
It's my problem,
I have to take care of it myself.

497
00:35:19,450 --> 00:35:20,290
All right then.

498
00:35:20,990 --> 00:35:21,830
Fighting!

499
00:35:22,500 --> 00:35:23,340
Fighting, Peak.

500
00:35:58,760 --> 00:35:59,600
Thanwa.

501
00:36:13,880 --> 00:36:15,240
Will he get scolded by his father?

502
00:36:17,110 --> 00:36:17,950
It's kind of like...

503
00:36:19,660 --> 00:36:20,950
"I don't accept you".

504
00:36:21,120 --> 00:36:22,310
"You are not my son".

505
00:36:22,430 --> 00:36:23,580
It will be like a drama.

506
00:36:23,770 --> 00:36:25,610
"What did you just say?"

507
00:36:26,080 --> 00:36:27,630
"My heart is hurting".

508
00:36:27,630 --> 00:36:28,730
"Call the ambulance now".

509
00:36:29,240 --> 00:36:30,550
Does Uncle have any congenital disease?

510
00:36:32,310 --> 00:36:33,450
Calm down, baby.

511
00:36:35,550 --> 00:36:38,080
This matter is not that serious.

512
00:36:40,270 --> 00:36:41,200
That's right.

513
00:36:41,760 --> 00:36:43,080
