514
00:36:45,360 --> 00:36:46,200
No.

515
00:36:46,650 --> 00:36:47,610
It's not "just".

516
00:36:48,670 --> 00:36:49,770
What did I just say?

517
00:36:51,290 --> 00:36:52,590
Thanwa, I am sorry.

518
00:36:52,830 --> 00:36:55,130
That I said about canceling the wedding.

519
00:36:55,130 --> 00:36:56,420
- Hold on.
- Wait, Thanwa.

520
00:36:57,830 --> 00:36:59,470
We have to let Peak and his father
discuss about this matter.

521
00:37:01,990 --> 00:37:03,660
Thanwa, I am sorry.

522
00:37:04,210 --> 00:37:05,260
I didn't mean to.

523
00:37:05,790 --> 00:37:06,630
- Calm down.
- Yes.

524
00:37:07,360 --> 00:37:08,370
Hey, Thanwa.

525
00:37:10,920 --> 00:37:12,000
I can let it go.

526
00:37:12,830 --> 00:37:14,710
But you have to let me go
to the restroom.

527
00:37:18,660 --> 00:37:19,580
Please go.

528
00:37:26,800 --> 00:37:27,640
Speaking of which,

529
00:37:28,150 --> 00:37:29,200
I want to go to the restroom too.

530
00:37:30,400 --> 00:37:31,240
You too?

531
00:37:42,650 --> 00:37:43,940
Did you sleep over with your friend?

532
00:37:45,360 --> 00:37:46,200
Yes.

533
00:37:46,930 --> 00:37:47,770
I am sorry.

534
00:37:49,000 --> 00:37:52,000
