so I didn't answer the calls.

535
00:37:53,860 --> 00:37:55,040
Are you sure he is just a friend?

536
00:38:01,030 --> 00:38:02,310
If he is not a friend,

537
00:38:03,600 --> 00:38:04,700
what would you say?

538
00:38:06,020 --> 00:38:06,860
Peak, you...

539
00:38:10,770 --> 00:38:12,120
