to confess.

543
00:38:19,680 --> 00:38:22,380
I know that I let everything
go with the flow to this point.

544
00:38:25,910 --> 00:38:27,530
Jane is my best friend.

545
00:38:28,330 --> 00:38:30,370
But she is not the person
who I love and want to marry.

546
00:38:37,050 --> 00:38:38,620
I want to cancel the wedding.

547
00:38:46,090 --> 00:38:47,100
