548
00:38:47,330 --> 00:38:49,260
Because I was afraid
if I said this in a wrong way,

549
00:38:50,560 --> 00:38:51,760
it would make you unhappy.

550
00:38:59,310 --> 00:39:01,040
We only have each other.

551
00:39:04,730 --> 00:39:06,250
If I ever loose you,

552
00:39:08,790 --> 00:39:10,820
